OL,3,CConcern Sark could depend on Guernsey
OL,4,Cif loan agreed for utility buyout
OL,6,FThe head of Sark Electricity Limited
OL,7,Fsays the island risks losing its
OL,8,Fpolitical independence after its Chief
OL,9,FPleas government asked Guernsey to
OL,10,Fborrow #1.5 million to buy the company.
OL,12,FThe States of Guernsey is willing to
OL,13,Foffer the loan in exchange for
OL,14,Fcommitments from Sark officials to
OL,15,Freview their tax regime, join a new
OL,16,Fpan-island body called the Bailiwick
OL,17,FCommission, and offer alcohol, fuel
OL,18,Fand tobacco duty as a financial
OL,19,Fguarantee.
