OL,6,FSuch a process would build a formal
OL,7,Fconstitutional relationship between
OL,8,Fthe two islands, something that has
OL,9,Fnever existed before.
OL,11,FSark was the last feudal state in
OL,12,FEurope, only moving from a fiefdom -
OL,13,Fwhere it was ruled by the Seigneur -
OL,14,Fto a democracy in 2008.
