OL,3,CConcern Sark could depend on Guernsey
OL,4,Cif loan agreed for utility buyout
OL,6,F"Such a change in Sark would, I
OL,7,Fbelieve, require a referendum, not a
OL,8,Fquiet conversation between friends
OL,9,Fover a coffee."
OL,11,FA letter, written by Guernsey's Policy
OL,12,Fand Resources Committee (P&R),
OL,13,Fexplains that Sark's Chief Pleas has
OL,14,Fasked for the loan to buy Sark
OL,15,FElectricity Limited so upgrades can be
OL,16,Fcarried out to the island's
OL,17,Felectricity grid.
