OL,6,FThe letter states: "The business case
OL,7,F(for issuing the loan) does not fit
OL,8,Fthe usual profile of investment
OL,9,Fdecisions by the States, but the
OL,10,Finvestment needs to be viewed on its
OL,11,Fsocial, rather than its commercial,
OL,12,Fmerits.
