OL,3,CConcern Sark could depend on Guernsey
OL,4,Cif loan agreed for utility buyout
OL,6,FConseiller Frank Makepeace adds: "It
OL,7,Fisn't just about money, it's about
OL,8,FSark becoming financially dependent on
OL,9,FGuernsey like Alderney and trading
OL,10,Faway our independence.
OL,12,F"What's worse is how it's all been
OL,13,Fhandled; the proposals have been
OL,14,Fpushed forward without the knowledge
OL,15,For consent of the majority of
OL,16,FConseillers and even many on the
OL,17,FPolicy and Finance Committee."
