OL,3,CConcern Sark could depend on Guernsey
OL,4,Cif loan agreed for utility buyout
OL,6,FIn response to the concerns,
OL,7,FConseiller Mike Locke explains: "I
OL,8,Fthink the conditions are perfectly
OL,9,Freasonable and not onerous.
OL,11,F"As far as the Bailiwick Commission is
OL,12,Fconcerned, it would have to be agreed
OL,13,Fby Chief Pleas and it is only advisory
OL,14,Fanyway.
OL,16,F"In terms of the Impot (tax), Guernsey
OL,17,Fcollects it for us anyway, so it's
OL,18,Fperfectly reasonable for it to be a
OL,19,Fbackstop and we are already doing a
OL,20,Ftaxation review."
