OL,4,Cif loan agreed for utility buyout
OL,6,FMr Witney-Price adds that Chief Pleas
OL,7,Fis trying to strike a deal from under
OL,8,Fhim, despite a #2.4 million sale
OL,9,Fhaving already been agreed with Island
OL,10,FPower, which he says is set to go
OL,11,Fthrough on 30 April.
OL,13,FThe Chair of Sark's Policy and Energy
OL,14,FCommittee, John Guille, says: "We've
OL,15,Fintroduced a compulsory purchase law
OL,16,Fin respect of the electricity assets,
OL,17,Fwhich is an option we don't want to go
OL,18,Fdown, but it's an option that's
OL,19,Favailable to us."
